               <p>The tools were taken out of a house building in <placeName id="t17540424-12-crimeloc61">Lincoln's-Inn-Fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17540424-12-crimeloc61" type="placeName" value="Lincoln's-Inn-Fields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17540424-12-crimeloc61" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540424-12-off60 t17540424-12-crimeloc61"></join>, betwixt Saturday night the 16th of March and the Monday morning, when the prosecutors going to work, they were missed. The prisoner being taken up for stealing two violins, and in goal, he confessed he had taken the tools mentioned, and pawned them to Mr. Singleton, where they were found, [produced in court and deposed to by the respective owners.] and Mr. Singleton deposed he took them in of the prisoner.</p>
